longBusinessSummary: EQS Group AG provides regulatory technology for corporate compliance and investor relations in Germany and internationally. It operates through two segments, Compliance and Investor Relations. The company offers global newswire, reporting, investor targeting and contact management, disclosure obligation, and insider list management services through its cloud-based platform EQS COCKPIT. It also provides whistleblowing and case management software; digital reports; and webcasting solutions, as well as investor relation website services. The company was formerly known as EquityStory AG and changed its name to EQS Group AG in June 2013. EQS Group AG was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Munich, Germany.
